{"tid":1187752,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(白色衫) 6月9日反「送中」大遊行 集合時間：2：30PM 起步時間：3：00PM（或維園草地達八成滿）","createTime":"2019-06-06T00:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T11:02:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"50238ace4b4c13cd82ab869f482304522513aa97","tid":1187752,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T00:46:52.000Z","msg":"(白色衫) 6月9日反「送中」大遊行 集合時間：2：30PM 起步時間：3：00PM（或維園草地達八成滿）<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線 Civil Human Rights Front<br />\n<br />\n6月9日反「送中」大遊行，最新安排如下：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">民陣呼籲當日著白色衫遊行</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">遊行起點：銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）</span><br />\n遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n集合時間：2：30PM<br />\n起步時間：3：00PM（或維園草地達八成滿）<br />\n<br />\n參與遊行呼籲：<br />\n<br />\n1. 想與民陣一同起步的遊行參與者，在維園草地集合。<br />\n<br />\n*2. 坐輪椅人士、有需要人士或推嬰兒車的照顧者，可以維園草地旁的「南路」集合，民陣會安排優先出發。<br />\n<br />\n3. 想中途加入遊行的參與者，可在軒尼斯道西行線（往灣仔方向，於銅鑼灣波斯富街之後的路段加入。但必須在帶頭車及遊行帶頭橫額之後，才加入遊行隊伍。）<br />\n<br />\n4. 請所有參與遊行的市民，就長時間遊行做好充足的準備，包括：水、毛巾、手機充電、雨傘、電風扇等等。<br />\n<br />\n無懼政權打壓，6月9日，全港總動員，反「送中」、撤惡法！<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線秘書處<br />\n<br />\n#遊行已獲發不反對通知書<br />\n#警方大石壓死蟹<br />\n#警權無限大<br />\n#人權被出賣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/61620734_2281134285267283_2809325987915890688_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=16575c49eeeb52ed852610bdb4b9c290&amp;oe=5D50D13E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F61620734_2281134285267283_2809325987915890688_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3D16575c49eeeb52ed852610bdb4b9c290%26oe%3D5D50D13E&h=f983196d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.680202458693815/2281134281933950/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2Fphotos%2Fa.680202458693815%2F2281134281933950%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElvMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=5bd1a243\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.680202458693815/2281134281933950/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"9ac5ca64b1a18625fb5912e4fe95e20fb6914f33","tid":1187752,"uid":216817,"like":0,"dislike":27,"score":-27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T00:53:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11dbf5744d1ef328f9485b02176d935fa61707de","tid":1187752,"uid":166250,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T01:29:09.000Z","msg":"各位小心有上次佔中嘅古惑仔出現挑釁警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我尋日發夢有人比錢請人6月9去遊行搞事"},{"pid":"43e419961a29cb334f0bcec1393352eb30e318cc","tid":1187752,"uid":14941,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:53:18.000Z","msg":"全家總動員去<br />\n加油！"},{"pid":"16dbd1f18c18df3df904a86c5252f832f774274c","tid":1187752,"uid":119478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T10:55:03.000Z","msg":"無白衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真唔明點解要跟dress code"},{"pid":"95e39920c7e2b7acddc789c9c6201da297bddd55","tid":1187752,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T14:52:09.000Z","msg":"大家遊行影相可以試下用呢個app，可以自己選擇加唔加 日期/時間/地點<br />\n<br />\n我都係最近遊行想落埋時間先搵到呢個 app, 大家盡早試吓點用， 其實我都唔係好熟， 求其見佢加到時間就收貨。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jeyluta.timestampcamerafree\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.jeyluta.timestampcamerafree&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElvMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=84333c86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jeyluta.timestampcamerafree</a><br />\n<br />\n最緊要 post 上嚟等大家了解各地點現場情況。"},{"pid":"407c01500482430d2a4e5e7d0dc3ed546f021b89","tid":1187752,"uid":252167,"like